= SDL_SensorGetType =

Get the type of a sensor.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
SDL_SensorType SDL_SensorGetType(SDL_Sensor *sensor);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''sensor'''
|The [[SDL_Sensor]] object to inspect
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns The SDL_SensorType type, or `SDL_SENSOR_INVALID` if `sensor` is
NULL.
